# Target: MiniMax-M3 block-sparse decode ATTENTION (`msa_sm100_decode`, in
# //Kernels/lib/msa) -- the kernel that attends the indexer-selected blocks
# (QK.softmax.V), distinct from the indexer (fuzzed by sparse_indexer_decode).
# Fuzzes batch + per-batch cache_length (biased non-BN-aligned) + topk; the
# last selected block is a PARTIAL local block whose tail (logical position >
